name: Pasta Carbonara
instructions: Boil pasta. Fry pancetta. Whisk eggs and cheese. Combine.

name: Chicken Curry
instructions: Sauté onions. Add chicken and spices. Simmer with coconut milk.

name: Vegetable Stir-fry
instructions: Chop vegetables. Stir-fry. Add sauce and noodles.

name: Scrambled Eggs
instructions: Whisk eggs. Melt butter. Cook eggs gently.

name: Lentil Soup
instructions: Sauté vegetables. Add lentils and broth. Simmer.

name: Chocolate Chip Cookies
instructions: Cream butter and sugar. Add eggs, mix dry ingredients. Fold in chocolate chips. Bake until golden.

name: Caesar Salad
instructions: Chop lettuce. Add croutons, cheese, and dressing. Add chicken if desired.

name: Tomato Soup
instructions: Sauté onions and garlic. Add tomatoes and broth. Simmer. Blend.

name: Guacamole
instructions: Mash avocados. Chop and add other ingredients. Mix well.

name: Pancakes
instructions: Whisk dry ingredients. Whisk wet ingredients. Combine. Cook on griddle.

name: Falafel
instructions: Soak chickpeas. Blend with herbs, onion, garlic, and spices. Form into patties and fry until golden.

name: Sushi Rolls
instructions: Cook sushi rice. Prepare fillings. Assemble rolls with nori, rice, and fillings. Slice and serve.

name: Gazpacho
instructions: Chop all vegetables. Blend with olive oil, vinegar, and a piece of bread until smooth. Chill well.

name: Beef Tacos
instructions: Cook ground beef with seasoning. Warm taco shells. Assemble tacos with beef and desired toppings.

name: French Toast
instructions: Whisk eggs, milk, cinnamon, and vanilla. Dip bread in mixture. Cook on griddle until golden. Serve with syrup and berries.

name: Pad Thai
instructions: Soak noodles. Stir-fry shrimp, tofu, and eggs. Add noodles, bean sprouts, and sauce. Garnish with peanuts and lime.

name: Hummus
instructions: Blend chickpeas, tahini, lemon juice, garlic, and cumin until smooth. Drizzle with olive oil.

name: Biryani
instructions: Marinate chicken. Layer rice, chicken, and fried onions with spices and herbs. Cook on low heat until done.

name: Mushroom Risotto
instructions: Sauté onion and garlic. Add rice and wine. Gradually add warm broth, stirring until absorbed. Stir in mushrooms, parmesan, and butter.

name: Smoothie
instructions: Combine all ingredients in a blender. Blend until smooth.
